nodes.text: 100 and Counting Expanded is an article by Pablo Hidalgo that appeared in Star Wars Insider 150. It serves as a guide for episodes of the fifth season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars, starting with "Eminence," and The Lost Missions, the series' final season at the time. This article is a follow-up to 100 and Counting published in Star Wars Insider 139, also listing the episodes in production order.
